title: I Love Inquirer
description: I wish I could just develop and then enter data in to command line tools. It reminds me of 10th grade in 1983. It's so refreshingly un-modern.

title: NPM Inquirer ROCKS!
description: You can ask like 50 questions and then painstakingly type your answers or use the arrow keys to select them!

title: Web Pages on Way Out
description: With command line tools and terminal - I do not think the world will use web pages much longer.
